metadata.description:
1 of 16
From PIC.SG (2013):

WHAT IS THE MERLION?
THE MERLION IS A HALF LION HALF FISH THAT LIVES IN SINGAPORE.

WHAT IS THIS SITE?
I THINK THE INTERNET DOES NOT HAVE ENOUGH PICTURES OF MERLIONS. SO I HAVE DRAWN THESE WITH MY LEFT HAND FOR THE BENEFIT OF SINGAPORE AND THE REST OF THE INTERNET. YEAH, I KNOW. NO, YOU DON'T HAVE TO THANK ME.
